{
  "stem": "15768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Because he and his wife were Romanian Jewish refugees.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They had no children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he made it his mission to get us on the road to our destination.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because he kept saying to my father, you have children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You have to make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They have to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "We're-- we're old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We have no family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "It's unimportant.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And so he gave my father money for whatever he needed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Their name was Spitter, Leon Spitter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think the wife was Henrietta Spitter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he went with my father as soon as the American consulate reopened to telegraph my family here in United States in New York, tell them that we were alive and that we were in dire need of money, as well as to again start working on the visa.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because all of our papers, when Antwerp and the lowlands were-- were bombed, the American consulate not only was bombed, but everything was lost.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was no trace of our visa or our tickets in order to sail.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no one to say, yes, indeed, we were headed in that direction.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to start really from square one, so to speak, at, a at the very beginning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, my good deed-- I had two deeds to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One of them was to look after Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Spitter, who was diabetic and couldn't resist French pastry and used to go out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had to sit with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she would invariably have a diabetic coma or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She would fall off the chair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was my job to see to it that she got home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We lived in a boarding house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a furnished room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The bath was in the hallway-- very French, very old, very dirty.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
